(72847, 187873, 6582, 3, 'psycho', '', '2014-02-27 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 1, '詞：鄭敬儒\n\n曲：楊尚樺/鄭敬儒/陳皇谷\n\n編曲：FUBAR\n\nWe tried to convince the outsiders that we are harmless butwe ended up in vain.\n\nWe sing we dance, we please and we begged, that’s how we died for live up our lives.\n\nWe scream we shout and we’re winning around. We drink up the liqueur and live with the rumors.\n\nUnder the light, psycho-like we cried. That’s how I look like, with or without the light.\n\nHere we go, breakdown the walls. Get out of control.', '', 225, '', '', '', '', 'Fubar樂隊', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-02-27 02:56:04', '2015-03-12 14:05:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
